quote_swap_in_tokens(uint256[],uint256[].notice: Quotes the amount of tokens required to be bought to swap NFTs for NFTs Tokens are required to pay for the redeem fee on swaps

set_addresses(address,address,address,ad.notice: Initializes the contract with the addresses of the vault, router, and tokens

stake_inventory(address,uint256[]).notice: Stakes an NFT in the vault

swap(uint256[],uint256[],address).notice: Swaps NFTs for NFTs by redeeming the NFTs for 1000 ERC20 tokens and swapping them for the target NFT

swap_eth_for_nft_v3(uint256[],address).notice: Swaps ETH for an NFT using the v3 router

swap_nft_for_eth_v3(uint256[],uint256,ad.notice: Swaps an NFT for ETH using the v3 router

unstake_inventory(address,uint256[]).notice: Unstakes an NFT from the vault
